operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">exec</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>plus<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"결과값을-출력해보면\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EA%B2%B0%EA%B3%BC%EA%B0%92%EC%9D%84-%EC%B6%9C%EB%A0%A5%ED%95%B4%EB%B3%B4%EB%A9%B4\" aria-label=\"결과값을 출력해보면 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>결과값을 출력해보면!</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"py\"><pre class=\"language-py\"><code class=\"language-py\"><span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">exec</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>plus<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token boolean\">None</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"하지만-할당--if--for-와-같은-구문을-넣으면-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%ED%95%98%EC%A7%80%EB%A7%8C-%ED%95%A0%EB%8B%B9--if--for-%EC%99%80-%EA%B0%99%EC%9D%80-%EA%B5%AC%EB%AC%B8%EC%9D%84-%EB%84%A3%EC%9C%BC%EB%A9%B4-1\" aria-label=\"하지만 할당  if  for 와 같은 구문을 넣으면 1 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>하지만, 할당 / if / for 와 같은 구문을 넣으면?</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"py\"><pre class=\"language-py\"><code class=\"language-py\"><span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">exec</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'answer = plus'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> answer\n<span class=\"token string\">'5+4'</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"py\"><pre class=\"language-py\"><code class=\"language-py\"><span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">exec</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"if plus: print('answer!')\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\nanswer!</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"py\"><pre class=\"language-py\"><code class=\"language-py\"><span class=\"token operator\">>></span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token keyword\">exec</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'for element in plus: print(element)'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">5</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">+</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">4</span></code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">이렇게 문자열로 이뤄진 &#39;식&#39; 을 받으면 None 을 반환하고,\n\n구문을 받으면 동작해요!</code></pre></div>\n<p><br><br><br></p>\n<h2 id=\"이-두-함수는\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%9D%B4-%EB%91%90-%ED%95%A8%EC%88%98%EB%8A%94\" aria-label=\"이 두 함수는 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>이 두 함수는,</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">파이썬의 내장 함수인데요!</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">인자로 주어진 문자열을\n\n파이썬의 컴파일 코드로 바꿔줘요!</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">파이썬의 인터프리터가 번역 / 실행할 수 있게 되요!</code></pre></div>\n<p><br><br><br></p>\n<h3 id=\"eval-은\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#eval-%EC%9D%80\" aria-label=\"eval 은 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>eval() 은,</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">실행시킨 결과를 반환해요!</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">반환을 할 수 있는 식이 아닌,\n\n실행을 해야하는 구문이 왔을 때,\n\n문법 오류를 일으켜요!</code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"exec-은\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#exec-%EC%9D%80\" aria-label=\"exec 은 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>exec() 은,</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">실행만 시켜요!</code></pre></div>\n<blockquote>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">식이나 구문에 대한 실행만 하고,\n\n결과값을 반환하지 않아,\n\nprint() 로 출력을 해도 None 을 반환해요!\n\n(단순히 실행만 했기 때문에, 실행한 결과값이 없으니까!)</code></pre></div>\n<p><br><br><br></p>\n<h2 id=\"상황에-따라서\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%83%81%ED%99%A9%EC%97%90-%EB%94%B0%EB%9D%BC%EC%84%9C\" aria-label=\"상황에 따라서 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>상황에 따라서,</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">실행의 결과값이 필요할 땐 eval() 함수를,\n\n구문의 실행동작만 필요할 땐 exec() 함수를 사용하면 좋겠죠?</code></pre></div>\n<p><br><br><br><br><br><br></p>\n<h2 id=\"eval-과-exec\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#eval-%EA%B3%BC-exec\" aria-label=\"eval 과 exec permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>eval() 과 exec(),</h2>\n<h1 id=\"매력적이지-않나요\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%A7%A4%EB%A0%A5%EC%A0%81%EC%9D%B4%EC%A7%80-%EC%95%8A%EB%82%98%EC%9A%94\" aria-label=\"매력적이지 않나요 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>매력적이지 않나요?</h1>\n<p><br><br></p>\n<h3 id=\"출처쓰\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B6%9C%EC%B2%98%EC%93%B0\" aria-label=\"출처쓰 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>출처쓰!</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://nan491.tistory.com/entry/Python-3-eval-%ED%95%A8%EC%88%98%EC%99%80-exec-%ED%95%A8%EC%88%98\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">’ YaluStar ’ 님의 티스토리 블로그 !</a></p>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/language/python/python_eval()-exec()","tagSlugs":["/tag/python/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2020-06-28","description":"문자열실행함수!","tags":["python"],"title":"파이썬에서 문자열을 실행시키기 !","socialImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/language/python/python_eval()-exec()"}}}